sentence: For example, Holmes falls in love and marries in Laurie R. King ' s Mary Russell series, is re-animated after his death to fight future crime in the animated series Sherlock Holmes in the 22nd Century, and is meshed with the setting of H. P. Lovecraft ' s Cthulhu Mythos in Neil Gaiman ' s A Study in Emerald (which won the 2004 Hugo Award for Best Short Story).
